uery the WebSocket Gateway\n  health               Fetch health from the running gateway\n  help                 Display help for command\n  hooks *              Manage internal agent hooks\n  logs                 Tail gateway file logs via RPC","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-taizi"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773842307928}}
