{"type":"message","id":"ea59c28a","parentId":"8b0838af","timestamp":"2026-03-18T13:58:53.053Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3dea43fc95ad45e09c3ce2eb","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.8 (3caab92) — I'm not AI-powered, I'm AI-possessed. Big difference.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents [options] [command]\n\nManage isolated agents (workspaces + auth + routing)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help    Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add           Add a new isolated agent\n  bind          Add routing bindings for an agent\n  bindings      List routing bindings\n  delete        Delete an agent and prune workspace/state\n  list          List configured agents\n  set-identity  Update an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\n  unbind        Remove routing bindings for an agent\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agents"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2212,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.8 (3caab92) — I'm not AI-powered, I'm AI-possessed. Big difference.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents [options] [command]\n\nManage isolated agents (workspaces + auth + routing)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help    Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add           Add a new isolated agent\n  bind          Add routing bindings for an agent\n  bindings      List routing bindings\n  delete        Delete an agent and prune workspace/state\n  list          List configured agents\n  set-identity  Update an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\n  unbind        Remove routing bindings for an agent\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agents","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-taizi"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773842333047}}
