{"type":"message","id":"bb4271dd","parentId":"caee0f1e","timestamp":"2026-03-18T13:58:56.739Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_432317c83f204e19b1999562","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.8 (3caab92) — Self-hosted, self-updating, self-aware (just kidding... unless?).\n\nUsage: openclaw acp [options] [command]\n\nRun an ACP bridge backed by the Gateway\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help               Display help for command\n  --no-prefix-cwd          Do not prefix prompts with the working directory\n  --password <password>    Gateway password (if required)\n  --password-file <path>   Read gateway password from file\n  --provenance <mode>      ACP provenance mode: off, meta, or meta+receipt\n  --require-existing       Fail if the session key/label does not exist\n                           (default: false)\n  --reset-session          Reset the session key before first use (default:\n                           false)\n  --session <key>          Default session key (e.g. agent:main:main)\n  --session-label <label>  Default session label to resolve\n  --token <token>          Gateway token (if required)\n  --token-file <path>      Read gateway token from file\n  --url <url>              Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                           when configured)\n  -v, --verbose            Verbose logging to stderr (default: false)\n\nCommands:\n  client                   Run an interactive ACP client against the local ACP\n                           bridge\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/acp"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2196,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.8 (3caab92) — Self-hosted, self-updating, self-aware (just kidding... unless?).\n\nUsage: openclaw acp [options] [command]\n\nRun an ACP bridge backed by the Gateway\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help               Display help for command\n  --no-prefix-cwd          Do not prefix prompts with the working directory\n  --password <password>    Gateway password (if required)\n  --password-file <path>   Read gateway password from file\n  --provenance <mode>      ACP provenance mode: off, meta, or meta+receipt\n  --require-existing       Fail if the session key/label does not exist\n                           (default: false)\n  --reset-session          Reset the session key before first use (default:\n                           false)\n  --session <key>          Default session key (e.g. agent:main:main)\n  --session-label <label>  Default session label to resolve\n  --token <token>          Gateway token (if required)\n  --token-file <path>      Read gateway token from file\n  --url <url>              Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                           when configured)\n  -v, --verbose            Verbose logging to stderr (default: false)\n\nCommands:\n  client                   Run an interactive ACP client against the local ACP\n                           bridge\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/acp","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-taizi"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773842336733}}
