{"type":"message","id":"bce79ad6","parentId":"0b1e4445","timestamp":"2026-03-18T13:59:23.836Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_23aec062ad6d44939c89ff8b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.8 (3caab92) — Your .zshrc wishes it could do what I do.\n\nUsage: openclaw agent [options]\n\nRun an agent turn via the Gateway (use --local for embedded)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>               Agent id (overrides routing bindings)\n  --channel <channel>        Delivery channel:\n                             last|telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line|feishu|nostr|msteams|mattermost|nextcloud-talk|dingtalk|matrix|bluebubbles|zalo|zalouser|synology-chat|tlon\n                             (omit to use the main session channel)\n  --deliver                  Send the agent's reply back to the selected channel\n                             (default: false)\n  -h, --help                 Display help for command\n  --json                     Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --local                    Run the embedded agent locally (requires model\n                             provider API keys in your shell) (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>       Message body for the agent\n  --reply-account <id>       Delivery account id override\n  --reply-channel <channel>  Delivery channel override (separate from routing)\n  --reply-to <target>        Delivery target override (separate from session\n                             routing)\n  --session-id <id>          Use an explicit session id\n  -t, --to <number>          Recipient number in E.164 used to derive the\n                             session key\n  --thinking <level>         Thinking level: off | minimal | low | medium | high\n  --timeout <seconds>        Override agent command timeout (seconds, default\n                             600 or config value)\n  --verbose <on|off>         Persist agent verbose level for the session\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"status update\"\n    Start a new session.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Summarize logs\"\n    Use a specific agent.\n  openclaw agent --session-id 1234 --message \"Summarize inbox\" --thinking medium\n    Target a session with explicit thinking level.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Trace logs\" --verbose on --json\n    Enable verbose logging and JSON output.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Summon reply\" --deliver\n    Deliver reply.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Generate report\" --deliver --reply-channel slack --reply-to \"#reports\"\n    Send reply to a different channel/target.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2222,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.8 (3caab92) — Your .zshrc wishes it could do what I do.\n\nUsage: openclaw agent [options]\n\nRun an agent turn via the Gateway (use --local for embedded)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>               Agent id (overrides routing bindings)\n  --channel <channel>        Delivery channel:\n                             last|telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line|feishu|nostr|msteams|mattermost|nextcloud-talk|dingtalk|matrix|bluebubbles|zalo|zalouser|synology-chat|tlon\n                             (omit to use the main session channel)\n  --deliver                  Send the agent's reply back to the selected channel\n                             (default: false)\n  -h, --help                 Display help for command\n  --json                     Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --local                    Run the embedded agent locally (requires model\n                             provider API keys in your shell) (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>       Message body for the agent\n  --reply-account <id>       Delivery account id override\n  --reply-channel <channel>  Delivery channel override (separate from routing)\n  --reply-to <target>        Delivery target override (separate from session\n                             routing)\n  --session-id <id>          Use an explicit session id\n  -t, --to <number>          Recipient number in E.164 used to derive the\n                             session key\n  --thinking <level>         Thinking level: off | minimal | low | medium | high\n  --timeout <seconds>        Override agent command timeout (seconds, default\n                             600 or config value)\n  --verbose <on|off>         Persist agent verbose level for the session\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"status update\"\n    Start a new session.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Summarize logs\"\n    Use a specific agent.\n  openclaw agent --session-id 1234 --message \"Summarize inbox\" --thinking medium\n    Target a session with explicit thinking level.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Trace logs\" --verbose on --json\n    Enable verbose logging and JSON output.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Summon reply\" --deliver\n    Deliver reply.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Generate report\" --deliver --reply-channel slack --reply-to \"#reports\"\n    Send reply to a different channel/target.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-taizi"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773842363827}}
{"type":"message","id":"b38a7dd6","parentId":"bce79ad6","timestamp":"2026-03-18T13:59:59.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！我可以使用 `openclaw agent --agent shangshu --message \"...\"` 来调用尚书省执行任务。\n\n让我构造任务消息并调用尚书省。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_79fdda62b24246b18a005d12","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agent --agent shangshu --message \"📮 中书省·任务令\n\n任务ID: JJC-20260318-002\n任务: 撰写Python快速排序算法说明文档\n门下省审议: ✅ 准奏\n审议意见:\n- 可行性：技术路径成熟，难度适中\n- 完整性：5项子任务覆盖核心需求\n- 风险：无明显风险点\n- 资源：中书省可独立完成\n\n执行方案（5项内容）:\n1. 算法原理与时间复杂度分析\n2. Python完整实现代码（含注释）\n3. 执行流程图解\n4. 代码运行示例\n5. 优化思路与应用场景\n\n输出要求:\n- Markdown格式文档\n- 包含完整Python代码和详细注释\n- 代码可直接运行验证\n\n请尚书省立即执行！\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai_zhongshu","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":590,"output":277,"cacheRead":16107,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16974,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773842363835}}
